@startuml m1_node_toolset_support_activity
' Research artifact (project-researcher) — toolset-support verification, not an HLD.
' One warning cycle across the four nodes, each step annotated with the tool that carries it.
title One warning cycle — each step on its picked toolset (R10 tick to R19 render)

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam wrapWidth 320

|#eef7ee|Bench — Python (+C++ encode)|
start
:R10 tick: advance A/B/C ground truth (Python engine);
:R13 LOS filter: own-sensor list excludes occluded C (Python geometry);
:R11 build B's CPM while C in B's gate (Python builder);
:R2 encode CPM — Vanetza ITS2 UPER (C++ component) or P1 JSON (Python);
:R12 apply seeded drop/delay/jitter pre-emission (Python);
:emit UDP datagram toward the V2X ECU adapter socket (Python stdlib socket);

|#eef2f7|V2X ECU — C++17|
:R5 adapter Rx: datagram from seam socket (POSIX/Asio UDP);
:R2/R7 decode CPM — Vanetza ITS2 asn1 codec (C++);
:R7 validate mandatory fields and ranges, dedupe (C++17);
:R7 map to R3 relayed object + B pose, forward JSON to ADA (C++ + JSON lib);

|#fdf6ec|ADA ECU — Python 3.11+|
:R15 admit v2x_relayed C into the track store (Python);
:R16 CRA plugin dispatch to the NLOS realization (Python);
:R17 compose d_AC, evaluate gate/TTC, set risk state (Python);
:R23 append risk event to JSONL evidence log (Python);
:R4 emit warning event + 10 Hz state over UDP JSON (Python stdlib socket);

|#f3eef7|IVI ECU — Kotlin on AAOS|
:R4 receive datagram in the foreground service (Kotlin DatagramSocket);
:parse versioned JSON, look up warningType registry (Kotlin);
:R18 shell state machine: idle to warning-view; heads-up if backgrounded (Compose + IMPORTANCE_HIGH CATEGORY_NAVIGATION);
:R19 render ghost C in 3D god view (SceneView/Filament) or 2D floor (Compose Canvas) behind the view seam;
stop

@enduml
